  <entry>
    <title>栈和队列</title>
    <url>/2022/01/28/%E6%A0%88%E5%92%8C%E9%98%9F%E5%88%97/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="栈和队列">栈和队列</h1>
<h2 id="栈">1.栈</h2>
<p><strong>栈</strong>(stack)是一个带有限制的表，它的插入和删除只能在一个位置上进行，即只能在表的末端进行，表的末端称为<strong>栈顶</strong>(top)</p>
<hr />
<h3 id="栈模型">1.1栈模型</h3>
<p>对栈的基本操作就是push(进栈)和pop(出栈)，前者等价于一次插入，后者则是删除最新插入的元素。最近插入的元素在执行pop之前可以通过使用top操作进行使用。在栈ADT中，对空栈执行top或pop一般均被认为是一个错误。另一方面，执行push时空间用尽是一个实现限制，但不是ADT错误。</p>
<hr />
<p>栈有时又叫作<strong>LIFO(后进先出)表</strong>，普通的清空栈操作和判断是否空栈的测试都是栈的操作指令系统的一部分，但是对栈所能够做的基本就是push和pop操作。</p>
<p><img
src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/AsukaMilet/BlogPhotos/master/Typora/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202022-01-28%20203951.png" /></p>
<center>
<p>
栈模型:通过push输入，通过pop和top输出
</p>
</center>
<p><img
src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/AsukaMilet/BlogPhotos/master/Typora/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202022-01-28%20205109.png" /></p>
<center>
<p>
栈模型：只有栈顶元素可访问
</p>
</center>
<hr />
<h3 id="栈的实现">1.2栈的实现</h3>
<h4 id="栈的stl实现">栈的STL实现</h4>
<p><a
href="https://www.cplusplus.com/reference/stack/stack/">STL中的Stack</a></p>
<h4 id="栈的数组实现">栈的数组实现</h4>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//C++ Version</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> Stack[MAX];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Initialization</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> top)</span>		<span class="comment">//清空栈</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    top=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">bool</span> <span class="title">IsEmpty</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> top)</span>				<span class="comment">//判断是否为空栈</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(top==<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">bool</span> <span class="title">IsFull</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> top)</span>				<span class="comment">//判断是否满栈</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(top==MAX<span class="number">-1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Push</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> num,<span class="keyword">int</span>*Stack)</span>		<span class="comment">//入栈</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(<span class="built_in">IsFull</span>(top))</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//报错</span></span><br><span class="line">    top++;</span><br><span class="line">    Stack[top]=num;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Pop</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> top)</span>					<span class="comment">//弹栈</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(<span class="built_in">IsEmpty</span>(top))</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//报错</span></span><br><span class="line">    top--;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">Top</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span>*Stack)</span>					<span class="comment">//返回栈顶元素</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> Stack[top];</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<hr />
<h3 id="栈的应用">1.3栈的应用</h3>
<ul>
<li><p>平衡符号<strong>(联机算法)</strong>：做一个空栈。读入字符直到文件尾。如果字符是一个开放符号('['、'{'等)，则将其推入栈中。如果一个字符是一个封闭符号，则当栈空时报错。否则，将栈元素弹出。如果弹出的符号不是对应的开放符号，则报错。在文件尾，如果栈非空则报错。</p>
<p><a
href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P1739">洛谷P1739</a></p></li>
<li><p>后缀表达式</p>
<p><a
href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P1449">洛谷P1449</a></p></li>
<li><p>中缀到后缀的转换</p></li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h3 id="单调栈">1.4单调栈</h3>
<p>单调栈即满足单调性的一种特殊栈结构</p>
<h4 id="插入">插入</h4>
<p>将一个元素插入单调栈时，为了维护栈的单调性，需要在保证将该元素插入到栈顶后整个栈满足单调性的前提下弹出最少的元素。</p>
<p>实现如下:</p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//插入X</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span>(!sta.<span class="built_in">empty</span>()&amp;&amp;sta.<span class="built_in">top</span>()&lt;X)</span><br><span class="line">    sta.<span class="built_in">pop</span>();</span><br><span class="line">sta.<span class="built_in">push</span>(X);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="使用">使用</h4>
<p>从栈顶读取元素，读取元素为栈中最大值或最小值</p>
<h4 id="应用">应用</h4>
<ul>
<li><p><a
href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P5788">洛谷P5788</a></p></li>
<li><p><a
href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P6198">洛谷P6198</a></p></li>
<li><p><a
href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P6510">洛谷P6510</a></p></li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h2 id="队列">2.队列</h2>
<p><strong>队列</strong>(queue)也是一种表。使用队列时插入在一端进行而删除则在另一端进行。</p>
<h3 id="队列模型">2.1队列模型</h3>
<p>队列的基本操作是enqueue(入队)，它是在表的末端(称为<strong>队尾</strong>(rear))插入一个元素，一个dequeue(出队)，它是删除(并返回)在表的开头(叫作<strong>队头</strong>(front))的元素。队列也被称为<strong>FIFO(先进先出)表</strong>。</p>
<p><img
src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/AsukaMilet/BlogPhotos/master/Typora/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202022-01-28%20215110.png" /></p>
<center>
<p>
队列模型
</p>
</center>
<hr />
<h3 id="队列的实现">2.2队列的实现</h3>
<h4 id="队列的stl实现">队列的STL实现</h4>
<p><a
href="https://www.cplusplus.com/reference/queue/queue/">STL中的队列</a></p>
<h4 id="队列的数组实现">队列的数组实现</h4>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// C++ Version</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> Queue[MAX];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> head,tail;						<span class="comment">//head表示队首，tail表示队尾</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Initialization</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> head,<span class="keyword">int</span> tail)</span>	<span class="comment">//清空队列</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    head=tail=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">bool</span> <span class="title">IsEmpty</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> head,<span class="keyword">int</span> tail)</span>			<span class="comment">//判断是否为空队列</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(head==tail)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">bool</span> <span class="title">IsFull</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> head,<span class="keyword">int</span> tail)</span>			<span class="comment">//判断队列是否已满</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(head==(tail+<span class="number">1</span>)%MAX)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Enqueue</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> num,<span class="keyword">int</span>*Queue)</span>			<span class="comment">//入队</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(<span class="built_in">IsFull</span>(head,tail))</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//报错</span></span><br><span class="line">    Queue[tail]=num;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(tail+<span class="number">1</span>==MAX)</span><br><span class="line">        tail=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">        tail++;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Dequeue</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> num,<span class="keyword">int</span>*Queue)</span>			<span class="comment">//出队</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(<span class="built_in">IsEmpty</span>(<span class="keyword">int</span> head,<span class="keyword">int</span> tail))</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//报错</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(head+<span class="number">1</span>==MAX)</span><br><span class="line">        head=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">        head++;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">Front</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> head,<span class="keyword">int</span>*Queue)</span>			<span class="comment">//取得队首元素</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> Queue[head];</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//若要实现双端队列操作，只需传入tail即可</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<hr />
<h3 id="队列的应用">2.3队列的应用</h3>
<ul>
<li><p><a
href="https://www.acwing.com/problem/content/134/">AcwingP132</a></p></li>
<li><p><a
href="https://www.acwing.com/problem/content/831/">AcwingP829</a></p></li>
<li><p><a
href="https://www.acwing.com/problem/content/3551/">AcwingP3548</a></p></li>
</ul>
<h3 id="单调队列">2.4单调队列</h3>
<p>单调队列中的元素应满足单调性<strong>递增</strong>或<strong>递减</strong>，且元素只能从队头与队尾进行操作。</p>
<h4 id="插入-1">插入</h4>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//插入X</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span>(!que.<span class="built_in">empty</span>()&amp;&amp;que.<span class="built_in">back</span>()&gt;X)			<span class="comment">//若队尾元素比待插入值大，循环弹出</span></span><br><span class="line">    que.<span class="built_in">pop_back</span>();</span><br><span class="line">que.<span class="built_in">push_back</span>(X);							</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="使用-1">使用</h4>
<p>队首元素为最大值或最小值</p>
<ul>
<li><p><a
href="https://www.acwing.com/problem/content/156/">AcwingP154</a></p></li>
<li><p><a
href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P2032">洛谷P2032</a></p></li>
<li><p><a
href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P1638">洛谷P1638</a></p></li>
</ul>
<hr />
<p>Author: AsukaMilet</p>
<p>Date: 2022-1-28</p>
]]></content>
