  <entry>
    <title>不相交集（DisjSets）的原理及实现</title>
    <url>/2022/01/26/%E4%B8%8D%E7%9B%B8%E4%BA%A4%E9%9B%86%EF%BC%88DisjSets%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E5%8F%8A%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1
id="不相交集disjsets的原理及实现">不相交集（DisjSets）的原理及实现</h1>
<h2 id="不相交集基本知识">1.不相交集基本知识</h2>
<p>不相交集主要涉及两种操作：合并和查找。初始时，不同的集合中元素不相交(<span
class="math inline">\(S_i \cap
S_j=\varnothing\)</span>),经过一系列Union操作后,合并为一个大的集合。</p>
<p>DisjSets是一种动态集合（随着Union操作的增多，动态集合中集合个数减少）
<span class="math display">\[
S=\{s_1,s_2,s_3....s_n\}
\]</span> 判断某个元素是否在集合<span
class="math inline">\(s_i\)</span>中,只需进行Find操作，返回值为包含给定元素集合的名字。判断两个元素是否在同一个集合中只需要比较Find(X)和Find(Y)是否返回同一个集合名字即可。</p>
<p>不相交集的应用范围：</p>
<ol type="1">
<li><strong><em>判断无向图的连通分量个数</em></strong></li>
<li><strong><em>判断无向图中任意两个顶点是否连通</em></strong></li>
<li>......</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="不相交集的基本实现c">2.不相交集的基本实现（C++）</h2>
<h3 id="class实现">（1）Class实现</h3>
<h4 id="adt接口实现一维数组实现">①ADT接口实现（一维数组实现）</h4>
<p>不相交集<strong>S</strong>由若干子集合<strong><span
class="math inline">\(s_i\)</span></strong>构成，不相交集的逻辑结构就是一个森林（树的集合）。<strong><span
class="math inline">\(s_i\)</span></strong>表示森林中的一颗子树，一般以该子树的根作为子树代表。</p>
<p>由于需要的唯一信息为<strong>父链（parent
link）</strong>，集合的名字由根处的节点给出，由于只需要知道父节点的名字，可以假设这棵树被非显式存储在一个数组中：数组的每个成员<strong>s[i]</strong>表示元素<strong>i</strong>的父亲，如果<strong>i</strong>为根，则<strong>s[i]=i</strong>（<em>e.g.</em>
s[5]=4，表示节点5的父亲为节点4）</p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">DisjSets</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">explicit</span> <span class="title">DisjSets</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> ElementsNum)</span></span>;   <span class="comment">//构造函数，初始化DisjSets</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">Find</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> num)</span></span>;                    <span class="comment">//Find操作</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">UnionSets</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> num1,<span class="keyword">int</span> num2)</span></span>;    <span class="comment">//Union操作</span></span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    vector&lt;<span class="keyword">int</span>&gt; s;</span><br><span class="line">    vector&lt;<span class="keyword">int</span>&gt; rank;					  <span class="comment">//保存每个子树的秩</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> count;                            <span class="comment">//记录DisjSets中子集合的个数（子树个数）</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>初始化操作如下：</p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">DisjSets::<span class="built_in">DisjSets</span>(<span class="keyword">int</span> ElementsNum)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="keyword">int</span> i=<span class="number">0</span>;i&lt;ElementsNum;i++)      <span class="comment">//若编号从1开始，则ElementsNum应为输入元素个数加1</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        s.<span class="built_in">push_back</span>(i);</span><br><span class="line">        rank.<span class="built_in">push_back</span>(<span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    count=ElementsNum;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<hr />
<h4 id="基本操作实现">②基本操作实现</h4>
<p>Union操作即将两个不相交的子集和合并成一个大集合,只需将一颗子树的父节点指向另一颗子树即可</p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">DisjSets::UnionSets</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> num1,<span class="keyword">int</span> num2)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> root1=<span class="built_in">Find</span>(num1);          <span class="comment">//查找num1元素的祖先</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> root2=<span class="built_in">Find</span>(num2);          <span class="comment">//查找num2元素的祖先</span></span><br><span class="line">    s[root2]=root1；               <span class="comment">//将num2祖先变为num1祖先的儿子</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>Find操作即查找所需元素所在集合，即返回所在元素名字。</p>
<p><strong><em>e.g</em></strong> 并查集如下：</p>
<p><img
src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/AsukaMilet/BlogPhotos/master/Typora/715283-20160917221621664-276304966.png" /></p>
<p>此时共有四个子树，第一个子树名字为0，第二个子树名字为1，第三个子树名字为3，第四个子树名字为5。所以Find(2)返回值为1，Find(4)返回值为3，Find(3)返回值为3。Find基本实现如下：</p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">DisjSets::Find</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> num)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(s[num]==num)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> num;                </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="built_in">Find</span>(s[x]);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<hr />
<h4 id="unionfind操作的改进">③Union/Find操作的改进</h4>
<h5 id="i.按高度秩rank求并">I.按高度（秩（rank））求并</h5>
<p>上述Union操作很随意：任选一颗子树，将另一颗子树的根指向它就完成合并。若一直按上述操作合并，可能产生非常不平衡的子树，如：</p>
<p><img
src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/AsukaMilet/BlogPhotos/master/Typora/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202022-01-26%20195423.png" /></p>
<p><strong>树变得越来越高，此时会影响到Find的效率</strong>。</p>
<p>因此引入按秩合并（启发式合并）：将秩小的子树的根指向秩大的子树的根。</p>
<p>秩的定义：对每个节点，用秩表示节点高度的上界（路径压缩不完全与秩兼容，路径压缩会改变树的高度，此时不追求树的高度的精确值，而是存储树的高度的估计值，树的高度的估计值为秩）</p>
<p>若不考虑路径压缩，则为<strong>按高度求并（union by
height）</strong>：在合并前，判断哪颗子树更高，让更矮的子树的根节点指向高的子树的根。</p>
<p>实现如下：</p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">DisjSets::UnionSets</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> num1,<span class="keyword">int</span> num2)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> root1=<span class="built_in">Find</span>(num1);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> root2=<span class="built_in">Find</span>(num2);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(root1!=root2)</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(rank[root1]&gt;rank[root2])                 <span class="comment">//num1所在子树更深</span></span><br><span class="line">        s[root2]=root1;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span>(rank[root1]&lt;rank[root2])            <span class="comment">//num2所在子树更深</span></span><br><span class="line">        s[root1]=root2;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            s[root2]=root1;                         <span class="comment">//将num2所在子树合并至num1所在子树</span></span><br><span class="line">            rank[root1]++;                          <span class="comment">//num1所在子树秩加深</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h5
id="ii.路径压缩核心思路将查找路径上节点直接连接至根上">II.路径压缩（核心思路：将查找路径上节点直接连接至根上）</h5>
<p>对于上述Find操作，对于连续M个指令（在所有模型下）平均为线性的。但<strong><em>O（M<span
class="math inline">\(\log{N}\)</span>）</em></strong>的最坏情况仍有可能发生。例如，把所有集合放于一个队列中，并反复让前两个集合出队而使它们的并入队，则最坏情况就会发生。路径压缩操作相对于基础Find操作变化不大，使s[<strong><em>num</em></strong>]等于由Find返回的值。这样，在集合的根被递归地查找到后，<strong><em>num</em></strong>的父节点就设置为它，这对通向根的路径上的每一个节点递归地出现，因而实现路径压缩。</p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">DisjSets::Find</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> num)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(s[num]==num)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> num;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> s[num]=<span class="built_in">Find</span>(s[num]);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h5
id="iii.路径压缩与按高度求并兼容问题">III.路径压缩与按高度求并兼容问题</h5>
<p>因为路径压缩可以改变树的高度，此时不清楚如何去重新计算树的高度，解决方案则是<strong>不计算树的高度</strong>，此时，对于每棵树所存储高度变为估计值（秩）。</p>
<p>若不使用按高度合并，只使用路径压缩最坏时间复杂度为<strong><em>O(m<span
class="math inline">\(\log{N}\)</span>)</em></strong>。</p>
<p>若只使用按高度求并，不使用路径压缩，时间复杂度为<strong><em>O(m<span
class="math inline">\(\log{n}\)</span>)</em></strong>，由于由于路径压缩单次合并可能造成大量修改，有时路径压缩并不适合使用。例如，在可持久化不相交集、线段树分治
+ 不相交集中，一般使用只按高度合并的不相交集。</p>
<p>时间复杂度与空间复杂度分析:</p>
<p><a href="https://oi-wiki.org/ds/dsu/">OI Wiki并查集</a></p>
<hr />
<h3 id="不相交集的数组实现">（2）不相交集的数组实现</h3>
<p>代码如下：</p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> DijsSets[MAX];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Initialization</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> size)</span>                 <span class="comment">//初始化DisjSets</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="keyword">int</span> i=<span class="number">0</span>;i&lt;size;i++)					  <span class="comment">//编号从0开始</span></span><br><span class="line">        DijsSets[i]=i;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">Find</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> num,<span class="keyword">int</span>*DisjSets)</span>                <span class="comment">//路径压缩查找</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(DisjSets[num]!=num)					  <span class="comment">//num不是该集合的根</span></span><br><span class="line">        DisjSets[num]=<span class="built_in">Find</span>(DisjSets[num],DisjSets);    <span class="comment">//递归搜索</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> num;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">UnionSets</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> num1,<span class="keyword">int</span> num2,<span class="keyword">int</span>*DisjSets)</span>         <span class="comment">//简单合并</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> root1=<span class="built_in">Find</span>(num1,DisjSets);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> root2=<span class="built_in">Find</span>(num2,DisjSets);</span><br><span class="line">    DisjSets[root2]=root1;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="不相交集应用">3.不相交集应用</h2>
<p>应用本质：初始时为一个个不连通的对象，经过一步步处理，变成连通的。</p>
<ol type="1">
<li><p><strong>生成迷宫</strong>：<img
src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/AsukaMilet/BlogPhotos/master/Typora/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202022-01-26%20195521.png" /></p>
<p><img
src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/AsukaMilet/BlogPhotos/master/Typora/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202022-01-26%20195539.png" /></p>
<p><img
src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/AsukaMilet/BlogPhotos/master/Typora/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202022-01-26%20195615.png" /></p></li>
<li><p><strong>无向图的连通分量个数</strong>：初始时，将无向图中各个顶点视为不连通的子集合，对图中每一条边，相当于union这条边对应的两个顶点分别所在的集合，直至所有的边都处理完后，还剩下的集合的个数即为连通分量的个数。</p></li>
</ol>
<hr />
<h2 id="相关题目">相关题目</h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P3367">洛谷P3367</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P1551">洛谷P1551</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P1621">洛谷P1621</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P2024">洛谷P2024</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P1196">洛谷P1196</a></li>
<li><a
href="https://www.acwing.com/problem/content/147/">AcwingP145</a></li>
</ul>
