    <title>图论基础</title>
    <url>/2022/01/27/%E5%9B%BE%E8%AE%BA%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="图论基础">图论基础</h1>
<h2 id="图的定义">1.图的定义</h2>
<ul>
<li>图是用来对对象之间的成对关系建模的数学结构，一个<strong>图(Graph)</strong>
<em>G=(V,E)</em>由"节点"或"顶点"(Vertex）以及连接这些顶点的"边"（Edge）组成。
<ul>
<li>对于一张图<strong><em>G=(V,E)</em></strong>,若存在另一张图<strong><em>H=(V',E')</em></strong>满足<strong><em>V'<span
class="math inline">\(\subseteq\)</span>V</em></strong>，且<strong><em>E'<span
class="math inline">\(\subseteq\)</span>E</em></strong>,则称<strong><em>H</em></strong>为<strong><em>G</em></strong>的<strong>子图(Subgraph)</strong>,记作<strong><em>H<span
class="math inline">\(\subseteq\)</span>G</em></strong>。</li>
</ul></li>
<li>每一条边就是一个点对<strong><em>(v,w)</em></strong>，其中<strong><em>v,w<span
class="math inline">\(\in\)</span>V</em></strong>。如果点对是有序的，那么图就叫作<strong>有向(directed)</strong>的。有向的图也被称为<strong>有向图(digraph)</strong>。图中的边在连接顶点时无需区分方向，则图为<strong>无向</strong>的，也称为<strong>无向图</strong>。
<ul>
<li>对于有向图<strong><em>G=(V,E)</em></strong>,它的<strong>反图(Transpose
Graph)</strong>指的是点集不变，每条边反向得到的图，即：若<strong><em>G</em></strong>的反图为<strong><em>G<span
class="math inline">\(^T\)</span>=(V,E')</em></strong>,则<strong><em>E'=</em></strong>
<strong>{(w,v)|(v,w)<span class="math inline">\(\in\)</span><em>E</em>
}</strong></li>
</ul></li>
<li>有时候边具有第三种成分，即<strong>权</strong>(weight)或<strong>值</strong>(cost)。边的<strong>权值</strong>记为<strong><em>w(v,w)</em></strong>。</li>
<li>顶点集合为<strong><em>V</em></strong>，边集合为<strong><em>E</em></strong>的图记为<strong><em>G=（V，E）</em></strong>，其顶点数为<strong><span
class="math inline">\(|V|\)</span></strong>,边数为<strong><span
class="math inline">\(|E|\)</span></strong>。</li>
<li>相邻顶点构成的顶点序列称为<strong>路径</strong>(path)，即一个顶点序列<span
class="math inline">\(w_1,w_2,w_3,...w_n\)</span>, 使(<span
class="math inline">\(w_i,w_{i+1}\)</span>)<span
class="math inline">\(\in\)</span><strong><em>E</em></strong>,且1<em><span
class="math inline">\(\leq\)</span></em> <em>i</em> <em><span
class="math inline">\(&lt;\)</span></em>
<em>N</em>。则一条路径的长为该路径上的边数，它等于<em>N-1</em>。起点若与终点相同，则称为<strong>环</strong>。</li>
<li>与顶点相连的边数称为<strong>度(Degree)</strong>，有向图的度又分为<strong>入度</strong>(以该顶点为终点)和<strong>出度</strong>(以该顶点为起点)。</li>
<li><strong>连通图</strong>：任意两个顶点都是连通的，即都可从第一个顶点到第二个顶点，也可以从第二个顶点到第一个顶点。
<ul>
<li>连通分量：无向图<strong><em>G</em></strong>的极大连通子图称为<strong><em>G</em></strong>的连通分量。极大连通子图：该子图为<strong><em>G</em></strong>的连通子图，如果再加入一个顶点，该子图不连通。</li>
</ul></li>
<li><strong>完全图</strong>：任意两个顶点间都有一条边，无向完全图共有
<strong><em>n<span
class="math inline">\(\times\)</span>(n-1)/2</em></strong>条边,有向完全图共有
<strong><em>n<span
class="math inline">\(\times\)</span>(n-1)</em></strong>条边。</li>
<li><strong>稀疏图</strong>：边数远小于完全图的图。
<strong>稠密图</strong>：边数接近于完全图的图</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<h2 id="图的存储表示c">2.图的存储（表示）(C++)</h2>
<h3 id="邻接矩阵">2.1邻接矩阵</h3>
<p>若有<strong><em>n</em></strong>个点，则开一个<strong><em>n<span
class="math inline">\(\times\)</span>​n</em></strong>的二维数组，其中一维表示起点，另一维表示终点，其存储的值可用于表示边的存在与否或者边的权值大小。</p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> Edge[MAX][MAX]					<span class="comment">//按边数表示</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Insert</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> v,<span class="keyword">int</span> w,<span class="keyword">int</span> value)</span>  <span class="comment">//将两个点建立关系</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    Edge[v][w]=value;			    <span class="comment">//表示有向图</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//无向图表示为Edge[v][w]=Edge[w][v]=value</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//若无权值，可用1表示有边，0表示无边</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>邻接矩阵的空间复杂度为<strong><em>O(N<span
class="math inline">\(^2\)</span>)</em></strong>，若图中点较多，则大概率超出内存限制。</p>
<h4 id="复杂度">复杂度</h4>
<ul>
<li>查询是否存在某条边<strong><em>O(1)</em></strong></li>
<li>遍历连接一个点的所有边<strong><em>O(N)</em></strong></li>
<li>遍历整张图<strong><em>O(N<span
class="math inline">\(^2\)</span>)</em></strong></li>
</ul>
<h4 id="应用">应用</h4>
<p>邻接矩阵只适用于没有重边(或重边可以忽略)的情况。其最显著的优点是可以查询一条边是否存在。</p>
<p>由于邻接矩阵在稀疏图上效率很低(尤其是在点数较多的图上，空间无法承受)，所以一般只会在稠密图</p>
<p>上使用邻接矩阵。</p>
<hr />
<h3 id="邻接表">2.2邻接表</h3>
<p>若有<strong><em>n</em></strong>个点，则开一个大小为<strong><em>n</em></strong>的vector数组，其中数组下标表示起点，vector中存储的值为终点</p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vector&lt;<span class="keyword">int</span>&gt;Edge[MAX];						 <span class="comment">//存储vector&lt;int&gt;的数组</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Insert</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> v,<span class="keyword">int</span> w)</span>					 <span class="comment">//无权值情况</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    Edge[v].<span class="built_in">push_back</span>(w);                    <span class="comment">//从v出发，到达终点为w</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>若边具有权值，则：</p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">Node</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> end;							      <span class="comment">//存储中终点</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> value;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">vector&lt;Node&gt;Edge[MAX];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Insert</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> v,<span class="keyword">int</span> w,<span class="keyword">int</span> value)</span>			  <span class="comment">//有权值情况</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    Node temp;</span><br><span class="line">    temp.end=w;</span><br><span class="line">    temp.value=value;</span><br><span class="line">    Edge[v].<span class="built_in">push_back</span>(temp);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="复杂度-1">复杂度</h4>
<ul>
<li>查询是否存在<strong><em>u</em></strong>到<strong><em>v</em></strong>的边<strong><em>O(d(u))</em></strong></li>
<li>遍历点<strong><em>u</em></strong>的所有出边<strong><em>O(d(u))</em></strong></li>
<li>遍历整张图<strong><em>O(M+N)</em></strong></li>
<li>空间复杂度<strong><em>O(M)</em></strong></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>P.S </strong>
<strong><em>d(u)</em></strong>为以<strong><em>u</em></strong>为出发点的所有边数</p>
<h4 id="应用-1">应用</h4>
<p>存各种图都很适合，除非有特殊需求（如需要快速查询一条边是否存在，且点数较少，可以使用邻接矩阵）。尤其适用于需要对一个点的所有出边进行排序的场合。</p>
<hr />
<h4 id="链式前向星">2.3链式前向星</h4>
<p>本质是静态的链表式存储</p>
<p><img
src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/AsukaMilet/BlogPhotos/master/Typora/1184092-20180710221842009-1426915822.png" /></p>
<p>基本结构如下：</p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">Node</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> end;								<span class="comment">//终点</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> value;								<span class="comment">//边的权值</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> next;								</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">Node Edge[MAX];</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ol type="1">
<li><strong>对于next</strong>:</li>
</ol>
<p>举个例子，从节点1出发，节点编号最大的是节点5，节点5的next将会是3，而节点3的next将会是结点2，而到了节点2之后节点1的所有出边都已经被处理了，所有节点2的next将会是-1，这样子将可以找到对于节点1的所有直接相接的节点（注意：遍历时节点是由大到小遍历的，即是逆序的）。当检测到next的值为-1时会退出当前遍历。</p>
<p>如果节点的出度为0或者小于1，则对应的next值为-1。</p>
<ol start="2" type="1">
<li><strong>对于end</strong></li>
</ol>
<p>简单概括来说就是对于第<strong>i</strong>条边的终点，比如说输入第一组边（1，
2）的时候，Edge[0].end = 2（数组从0开始存储）。</p>
<p>如果是有向图，那么只要处理一次就够了。对于一个无向图的话，就需要来回存一次。</p>
<ol start="3" type="1">
<li><strong>对于head数组</strong></li>
</ol>
<p>对于输入的边，用来存以<strong>i</strong>为起点的边的存储位置。如果以<strong>i</strong>为起点的边出度大于1，此时head[i]会存入在输入中最后输入的以<strong>i</strong>为起点的编号。</p>
<p><strong><em>e.g</em></strong>
对于节点1，它的出度为3，由先往后分别输入了（1， 2）（1， 3）（1，
5），最后存入head的就会是5（2和3其实也有被存储的时候，但是后来会被5覆盖掉），即结果就是head[1]
= 5。</p>
<p>建立边方式如下：</p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//head[u]和k的初始值均为-1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Insert</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> v,<span class="keyword">int</span> w,<span class="keyword">int</span> value)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    Edge[k].end=w;</span><br><span class="line">    Edge[k].value=value;</span><br><span class="line">    Edge[k].next=head[v];</span><br><span class="line">    head[v]=k++;					<span class="comment">//存储v这个值在第几组输入的边内出现过</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="复杂度-2">复杂度</h4>
<ul>
<li>查询是否存在<strong><em>u</em></strong>到<strong><em>v</em></strong>的边<strong><em>O(d(u))</em></strong></li>
<li>遍历点<strong><em>u</em></strong>的所有出边<strong><em>O(d(u))</em></strong></li>
<li>遍历整张图<strong><em>O(M+N)</em></strong></li>
<li>空间复杂度<strong><em>O(M)</em></strong></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>P.S </strong>
<strong><em>d(u)</em></strong>为以<strong><em>u</em></strong>为出发点的所有边数</p>
<h4 id="应用-2">应用</h4>
<p>存各种图都很适合，但不能快速查询一条边是否存在，也不能方便地对一个点的出边进行排序。</p>
<hr />
<h2 id="图的遍历">3.图的遍历</h2>
<p>图的遍历与搜索一样，主要分为<strong>DFS(深度优先搜索)</strong>与<strong>BFS(广度优先搜索)</strong></p>
<h3 id="dfs图论">3.1DFS(图论)</h3>
<p><strong>DFS的特点是，顺着当前的路径一直往深处遍历，直到无点可访问时，再返回上一级节点。</strong>DFS
会对其访问过的点打上访问标记，在遍历图时跳过已打过标记的点，以确保
<strong>每个点仅访问一次</strong>。符合以上两条规则的函数，便是广义上的
DFS。</p>
<p><strong><em>e.g</em></strong> <a
href="https://blog.csdn.net/saltriver/article/details/54429068">DFS(图论)图解</a></p>
<p>以邻接表为例:</p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//假设图的边有权值</span></span><br><span class="line">vector&lt;Node&gt;Edge[MAX];                               <span class="comment">//邻接表</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">bool</span> visited[MAX];					<span class="comment">//存储节点是否被访问过</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Dfs</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> start)</span>					<span class="comment">//start为开始访问节点</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    visited[start]=<span class="literal">true</span>;			<span class="comment">//将开始节点设置为已访问</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="keyword">int</span> i=<span class="number">0</span>;i&lt;Edge[start].<span class="built_in">size</span>();i++)	      <span class="comment">//遍历当前节点可到达的所有终点</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> next=Edge[start][i].end;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(visited[next]==<span class="literal">false</span>)</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">Dfs</span>(next);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//若next指向的节点尚未访问，则递归下去进行访问</span></span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="复杂度-3">复杂度</h4>
<p>时间复杂度通常为<strong><em>O(M+N)</em></strong>,空间复杂度为<strong><em>O(N)</em></strong>,N为图的点数，M为图的边数。</p>
<h3 id="bfs图论">3.2BFS（图论）</h3>
<p><strong>BFS的特点是，将当前所在节点可访问的所有节点都加入队列，等全都访问过后再前往下一层。</strong>BFS
算法找到的路径是从起点开始的<strong>最短</strong>合法路径。换言之，这条路径所包含的边数最小。</p>
<p><strong><em>e.g.</em></strong> <a
href="https://blog.csdn.net/saltriver/article/details/54428983">BFS(图论)图解</a></p>
<p>以邻接表为例：</p>
<figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//假设图的边有权值</span></span><br><span class="line">vector&lt;Node&gt;Edge[MAX];					        <span class="comment">//邻接表</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">bool</span> visited[MAX];						<span class="comment">//存储节点是否被访问过</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Bfs</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> start)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    queue&lt;<span class="keyword">int</span>&gt; q;						<span class="comment">//访问队列</span></span><br><span class="line">    q.<span class="built_in">push</span>(start);</span><br><span class="line">    visited[start]=<span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(!q.<span class="built_in">empty</span>())</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> now=q.<span class="built_in">front</span>();</span><br><span class="line">        q.<span class="built_in">pop</span>();</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="keyword">int</span> i=<span class="number">0</span>;i&lt;Edge[now].<span class="built_in">size</span>();i++)</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">int</span> next=Edge[now][i].end;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span>(visited[next]==<span class="literal">false</span>)</span><br><span class="line">            &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                q.<span class="built_in">push</span>(next);</span><br><span class="line">                visited[next]=<span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="复杂度-4">复杂度</h4>
<p>时间复杂度<strong><em>O(M+N)</em></strong>,空间复杂度<strong><em>O(N)</em></strong>。</p>
